title: Mystery Train
description: Finn and Jake get wrapped up in a high speed whodunit!

title: El dia divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: The Trouble with Truth
description: The JLA find themselves in danger of losing Wonder Woman when the goddess Athena comes to Earth with an offer Diana can't refuse, filling the position of the Goddess of Truth on Mt. Olympus.

title: Dinner at the Creek
description: Bernard is left in charge for the evening, so Craig sets out to find his own dinner at the creek.

title: Planet X
description: When Rad returns to his home planet, he learns a shocking truth about alien society.

title: The Explorer's Club
description: The ninja must break into the Explorer's Club to obtain the second Scroll of Forbidden Spinjitzu, running afoul of the club's manager and irate club-members.

title: La Dama
description: Los niños descubren que Papá se ha vestido como una mujer para conocer amigos.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Babysitting Bedlam/Rubbed the Wrong Way
description: Rubbed the Wrong Way: After a Bakugan field errupts the town kids stampede to get their own Bakugan but when the field is contaminated Lia must save the day./Babysitting Bedlam: Dan and Wynton meet a strange boy who leads them into an underground maze where they discover the boy's Bakugan has been enslaved.

title: The Bluster Bunch
description: A trail of tornadic destruction leads Mega Man, Suna, and Rush through a series of encounters with Air Man's quirky siblings.

title: Saving Faith
description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Benson's Suit
description: Benson wants to feel better about himself.

title: Earthlings
description: Amethyst tries to exact revenge with a showdown in the Kindergarten.

title: San Diego Comic-Con Official Steven Universe Panel
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar, Estelle, DeeDee Magno Hall, and Michaela Dietz discuss Steven Universe and its upcoming movie in this San Diego Comic-Con panel, hosted by Shelby Rabara.

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: California King
description: Rigby wins a king-size bed and throws his trampoline bed in the garbage. But when he realizes that he can't sleep without his trampoline, he has to go through an elaborate junkyard to find it.

title: Let's Team Up Because We Aren't Bad Friends
description: The Warriors fear that they've been ignoring their pals, so they team up with Witchy Simone and Noville for a BIG MISSION, only to discover that their friends aren't into it anymore.

title: Princess Buttercup
description: When Buttercup starts spending a lot of time with her new friends, a group of bad-girl skaters called The Derbytantes, it seems the Powerpuff Girls are down to two, which delights Princess Morbucks, who wants to fill the empty slot.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: El eslabon mas debil
description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.

title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

title: Are You Talking to Tree?
description: When the tree inside the RV begins talking to Uncle Grandpa, he must convince the gang that he's not going crazy.

title: Omni-Copped
description: When Grandpa Max's engineer buddy Phil Billings gifts Team Tennyson the Omni-Copter, a state of the art flying vehicle that can transport the Rustbucket for overseas adventures, Steam Smythe takes to the skies to ground Ben and company's first test flight; but unbeknownst to our heroes, Smythe was sent to battle Ben's latest alien forms by a mysterious, powerful enemy: the Forever Knight.

title: Chata's Quinta Quinceañera
description: Vic and Val want to go to a friend's pool party on the same day as their grandma's quinceañera, so they use a magical flute that allows them to teleport and attend both at the same time.

title: Steven Universe The Movie - True Kinda Love Official Music Video
description: : The official music video for "True Kinda Love" by Estelle feat. Zach Callison from Steven Universe The Movie.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 1
description: Optimus Prime and the Autobots battle Megatron and the Deceptions on Earth's Moon.

title: Let's Meet Sonic
description: When world class hero SONIC THE HEDGEHOG visits the plaza, he teams up with KO to save the day.

title: In the Wild/Call Me Old Brakken
description: In the Wild: The AO are invited to a video-stars conference, but when the chartered jet goes down, the AO must give over to their wild sides to survive!/Call Me Old Brakken: Lord Brakken is the ultimate AO super-fan, but his zeal takes a dark turn when he looks to prove that he is their superior in battle.

title: Aluxes
description: When Vic finds an ancient relic that summons a gang of mischievous creatures, he uses them to do his bidding, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Unboxing Part 1
description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

title: The Pact
description: Gumball finds Penny's laugh annoying, but can't think of a way to tell her without offending her. When he discovers that Principal Brown has the same problem with Miss Simian's morning breath, they decide to swap problems to save themselves from getting dumped.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Stratified/Maze Daze
description: Stratified: The AO embark on a mission into the mysterious labyrinth world of Vestroia to find Strata the Hunter and free the Bakugan he has imprisoned./Maze Daze: Lost in the maze of Vestroia the AO encounter powerful forces that seem to be struggling for control over the alien landscape.

title: Matter of the Mind/Core Cell
description: Matter of Mind: Drago leads the Bakugan against the threat of Tiko to protect a powerful energy source called the Core Cell./Core Cell: The AO defend the Core Cell from an attack by Tiko and in a last ditch effort to save it Dan manages to evolve Drago into his L2 form.

title: Bet to Be Blonde
description: Rigby wins a bet with Mordecai and makes him get a blonde perm.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Skater Sumo
description: As Sumo and Clarence are playing outside, Chelsea and Rita skate by on their new skateboards. Enthralled, Sumo decides to build his own and join their skating team, while Clarence seems to have other ideas.

title: The Forbidden Isle/New World Orders
description: The Forbidden Isle: The AO travel to a remote island in search of a Core Cell, but instead they find the Bakugan known as Kelion, which soon bonds with Dan./New World Orders: The AO discover a small group of kids and Bakugan being used as laborers against their will, but freeing them is only half the problem.

title: Friend Ship
description: The Crystal Gems explore an ancient Gem spaceship.

title: The More Things Change Part 1
description: Now on his own, Ben sets out to be a solo superhero, with new alien heroes at his disposal, but Grandpa Max has other plans. (Introducing Rook, Malware, Khyber, Nemetrix alien Crabdozer, new Ben aliens Feedback & Blox, Pakmar.)

title: Artesanias traviesas
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic libera al señor de las travesuras del interior una reliquia antigua, V y V tienen que trabajar en equipo para volver a encerrarlo.

title: #GothamCon
description: A fun day for Barbara Gordon and her bestie Harleen Quinzel (at Gotham City's annual geekfest, the Annual Convention of Gotham City Enthusiats!) is turned on its head when, out of nowhere, the villainous Harley Quinn shows up to wreak havoc! Lucky for everyone, Batgirl just happens to be in the area...

title: Mo' Linguish/Oops I Did It Again
description: Mo' Linguish: Mojo is sentenced to do community service for Townsville and begins teaching English at the Learning Annex. Soon everyone is speaking in circles like Mojo and the town comes to a standstill./Oops I Did It Again: When the Professor realizes that all his successful experiments are actually just accidents, he sets out to do something brilliant on purpose!

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Stay Goth, Poodle Girl, Stay Goth
description: Gwen accidentally brings a pink stuffed pony she loves to daycare and spends the day denying it's hers.

title: Plant Daddies
description: When Ms. Baker pairs up the kids to act as parents for a sprout, Sumo and Clarence learn all about good parenting. Jeff buys toys instead of fertilizer and Chelsea and Kimby get to know each other.

title: Fire!
description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

title: Mxy's Mix-Up
description: As the Justice League is trying to protect the United Nations from Grodd's gorilla army, Mr. Mxyptlk pops up from the fifth dimension and thinks it would be great fun to put each of the superheroes' brains into another hero's body.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: The Takeout Mission
description: Kelsey leads her friends on the most important quest ever, picking up takeout for dinner.

title: Dog Daze/In Focus
description: Dog Daze: Lightning discovers a new Bakugan, Artulean, leading to an unhealthy rivalry with Howlkor./In Focus: While Lia's newswoman mom does an expose on the AO Strata the Hunter tries to capture Hydorous.

title: Third Time's a Charm
description: Charmaster returns to exact her revenge on Gwendolyn once and for all.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Folk Art Foes
description: When Vic accidently unleashes the lord of mischief from an ancient relic, V and V have to work together to trap it back inside.

title: Popularity Conquest
description: When Mao Mao discovers that he is not as popular as Badgerclops and Adorabat, they decide to reinvent him as a kinder, cuddlier hero.

title: #BeastsInShow
description: When Babs and Kara spar over whose dog is better, they decide to settle it at the Metropolis Dog Show, where Ace the Bat-Hound and Krypto the Superdog suddenly find themselves called upon to save the day… in more ways than one.

title: Poles Apart
description: A trip to the South Pole goes upside down when Team Tennyson lands on the North Pole instead, but Ben quickly discovers the culprits: Solar & Polar Twain, magnetically-powered scientists who want to hold the world ransom by threatening to reverse Earth's magnetic poles!

title: Flower Power
description: Mega Man must battle Wood Man for the fate of the Corpse Flower, a rare and noxious bloom that's stinking up all of Silicon City.

title: This Spells Disaster
description: The gang is planning a surprise for Puppycorn, so they spell things out when talking so he won't find out. Desperate to know what they're saying, Puppycorn finds a magic book that he thinks will help him learn to spell, but unbeknownst to him, it's teaching him how to cast spells! Will Puppycorn realize that knowledge is power and some secrets are kept for a reason?

title: Ghosthaste
description: Vambre becomes enamored of a poltergeist within Ghost Magisword and Prohyas must save her before his sister becomes a ghost herself!

title: Blast Resort
description: Mega Man must assist Blasto Woman in a heist to stop a powerful EMP emitter from falling into the wrong hands.

title: Sigue la corriente
description: Cuando Sal se queda en lo de Vic y Val, los chicos no lo soportan como compañero, pero finalmente descubren lo genial y mágico que es.

title: A Jolt from the Past
description: Alien pests from Ben's youth come back, but now they need Ben's help. (Introducing Fistrick, & new Ben alien Gravattack.)

title: Vengeance Is Mine!
description: Aspheera arrives at the Monastery of Spinjitzu and confronts Wu, forcing one of the ninja to make a heroic sacrifice.

title: The Weakest Link
description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: El Gimnasio
description: Un millonario excéntrico adopta a los Osos bebé y los lleva a vivir a su mansión.

title: Hoofin' It
description: It's time for the annual Aberdale Greased Pig Chase and everyone's excited except Clarence. He feels so bad for poor little pig Butterscotch that he takes her place in the pig chase, running from townsfolk eager to take home the prized barrel full of hot dogs!

title: Ranger Norm
description: When Tabes leaves for a conference, the Bears have to deal with her substitute, Ranger Norm.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: Quintos Quinces
description: Victor y Valentino quieren ir a la fiesta en la piscina de un amigo el mismo día que la fiesta de quince años de su abuela, así que usan una flauta mágica que les permite teletransportarse y asistir a ambas al mismo tiempo.

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.

title: Framing Device/Bad Actors
description: Framing Device: When confronted by China Riot Lia learns to evolve Pegatrix after realizing the true meaning behind her filming obsession./Bad Actors: Dan tries to lie about evolving Drago and gets exposed while the team face off against Duran Dane and his unhappy Bakugan Nillious.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Nemesis
description: A shadowy figure named Peace Master targets the Candy Kingdom elite.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Recuerdos Locos
description: Cuando Perricornio ve a Unikitty hacer la cosa más vergonzosa de la historia, jura que nunca lo olvidará. Desesperada, Unikitty utiliza la máquina de memoria de la Dra. Fox para borrar el recuerdo de Perricornio del embarazoso evento. En el proceso, Unikitty libera accidentalmente todos los recuerdos de Perricornio. Ahora ella y su pandilla deben capturar todos los recuerdos de prisa, o Perricornio olvidará su vida.

title: Burbuja
description: Panda comienza a sufrir de fobia a los gérmenes y decide vivir el resto de su vida en una burbuja.

title: Dawn Before Dusk
description: Dawn Before Dusk, Part 1: The AO meet Benton Dusk discovering that their quiet little corner of the world is about to become much, much larger./Dawn Before Dusk, Part 2: Benton Dusk reveals that the AO have been indentified as persons of interest by powerful corporations including Philomena Dusk's AAAnimus.

title: Dead Ringer
description: When Vic doesn't pick Val for his soccer team, Val vows to win with his own squad. But when his team doesn't match up, he resorts to supernatural means to win.

title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

title: Letras Desastrosas
description: La pandilla está planeando una sorpresa para Puppycorn, así que deletrean las cosas cuando hablan para que él no se entere. Desesperado por saber lo que dicen, Puppycorn encuentra un libro mágico que cree que lo ayudará a aprender a deletrear, ipero sin saberlo, el libro le enseña a lanzar hechizos! ¿Se dará cuenta Puppycorn de que el conocimiento es poder, y de que algunos secretos se guardan por una razón?

title: Future Boy Zoltron
description: Steven fills in for a fortune teller at Funland.

title: Pool Duel
description: Unikitty and the gang are having a great time at the public pool, until they try to get Puppycorn to swim in the deep end with them. Puppycorn is terrified of the deep end. Now Unikitty and the gang must get him over his fear, so he can have maximum pool fun. Meanwhile, Master Frown and Brock are hatching a plan to ruin everyone's fun, by pulling the pool's plug.

title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Omnicoptero
description: Cuando el ingeniero Phil Billings, amigo del Abuelo Max, le regala al equipo Tennyson el Omni-Copter, un vehículo volador de última generación que puede transportar el Rustbucket hasta aventuras en el extranjero, Vapor Smythe sube a los cielos para obligar a aterrizar el primer vuelo de prueba de Ben y su familia. Pero sin que nuestros héroes lo sepan, Smythe fue enviado a combatir las formas alienígenas más nuevas de Ben por un misterioso y poderoso enemigo: el Caballero por Siempre.

title: The Secret of Dos Santos
description: Ben and Rook join Kai Green on a perilous alien relic hunt through South America.

title: Memory Amok
description: When Puppycorn witnesses Unikitty do the most embarrassing thing ever, he vows he will never forget it. Desperate, Unikitty uses Dr. Fox's memory machine to erase Puppycorn's memory of the embarrassing event. In the process, Unikitty accidentally releases all of Puppycorn's memories. Now she and the gang must scramble to capture all the scampering memories, or Puppycorn will forget his life.

title: The Great Disaster
description: Robin gets amnesia and starts thinking that Hawkman is his mother.

title: Keen on Keane/Not So Awesome Blossom
description: Keen on Keane: It's Valentine's Day and the girls notice that Ms. Keane is all alone. Time for a little matchmaking, but who will be the lucky fella?/Not So Awesome Blossom: When Blossom's attack plans fail one after the other, she loses confidence in herself as the group's leader.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.

title: King of the Zombeez
description: Frostferatu hires the Warriors to rid his castle of Zombeez when Neddy and a power mad zombie-bee queen take over.

title: Field Trippin'
description: After a pit stop bathroom break during a school field trip, Clarence returns to the parking lot and accidentally gets on the wrong school bus - which takes him to a different school!

title: Hot Air Buffoon/Ploys R' Us
description: Hot Air Buffoon: The Mayor realizes the girls are doing all the work in his city for him. So he mans a hot air balloon and starts fighting crime the old-fashioned way./Ploys R' Us: The girls wake up to find their room filled with toys. They soon figure out that the Professor has been sleepwalking and stealing. Instead of reporting it, the girls take advantage of the situation.

title: Sea of Tranquility Part 2
description: The Autobots struggle to stop the Decepticon's planet-cracking weapon as it targets Earth.

title: Painbow
description: When a mysterious rainbow causes everyone to become unnaturally happy, the Powerpuff Girls must find where it ends to save the day and return Townsville to normal.

title: Thumb War
description: The gang decide to compete in the annual Thumb War competition, but a surprise forces Mao Mao to deal with the unthinkable... losing.

title: A Real Steal/Lightning Unleashed
description: A Real Steal: Dan embarks on a solo adventure to outdo Magnus's new team of Bakugan Brawlers and winds up having to be saved by them instead./Lightning Unleashed: Lightning uncovers the Mind Core Cell buried beneath the Earth and battles Stata the Hunter in an effort to protect its secret.

title: Watch It!
description: The Powerpuff Girls are tasked with keeping a priceless gem safe from thieves.

title: All Jungled Up/Outer Demons
description: All Jungled Up: Still lost in Vestroia the AO experience mind altering effects of the nearby Core Cell and come face to face with the Bakuzon monster Tiko./Outer Demons: The AO find the doorway out of Vestroia only to learn they have entered a mirror world of their own imagining created by the Core Cell.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: Radical Rescue
description: Rad is forced to reconsider his identity when KO starts taking on some of his traits.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: A New Life
description: Apple and Onion both leave their homes and follow their dreams to the big city but things don't go quite to plan.

title: Convencion de Rath
description: De regreso en casa, Ben no puede inscribirse en un concurso de cosplay de gatos sin su propio disfraz. Pero cuando se convierte en Rath, un nuevo alienígena con aspecto felino y mal carácter, el lado salvaje que Ben acaba de descubrir pronto tendrá resultados inesperados.

title: The Throw Down/Brawl for It All
description: The Throw Down: Lightning reveals his discovery of the Mind Core Cell but the AO arrive only to discover that Magnus has already beaten them to it./Brawl for It All: With both team's Bakugan knocked into a hibernation state by the Mind Core Cell only Dan and Magnus remain locked in a brawl for it all!

title: Lecciones para un maestro
description: Cuando el Barón de Hierro obliga a Wu a tomar la Armadura de Dragón, las cosas no salen como se planearon. En Ninjago, hay un límite de lo que Lloyd puede soportar mientras se aferra a la esperanza del regreso de los Ninjas.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Primera parte
description: En el episodio estreno de cuatro partes de la serie, seis chicas comunes y corrientes se conocen y descubren que tienen poderes extraordinarios. Deciden unir sus fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: The Exit/The Lost and the Cost
description: The Exit: The AO compete with a rival Brawling team for ViewTube hits leading to a "winner take all" brawl./The Lost and the Cost: Everett Ray, a promotor, tries to get the AO to join an official league for Bakugan Battling.

title: The Perfect Team
description: Onion worries his relationship with Apple is in jeopardy when a stray cat enters the picture.

title: Full Disclosure
description: Steven tries to avoid Connie so he doesn't have to tell her about his most recent harrowing adventure.

title: Tripped Up/Power Tripp
description: Tripped Up: Dan and Wynton stumble on both a possible hidden location of the Mind Core Cell and Colonel Tripp who wants the energy source for himself./Power Tripp: After a falling out with Dan, Wynton is mind-controlled by Tripp who stages an attack to ignite a war between Brawlers and the Military.

title: El Tonto
description: Darwin termina en la sala de detención con el Chico Bomba, que decide convertir a Darwin en su nuevo blanco. Sin embargo, el ataque se vuelve en su contra cuando Darwin le arruina la vida.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: #SweetJustice Part 2
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: All By Mao Self
description: Mao Mao's desire to be a legend drives him to keep topping himself. But how much is enough?

title: Camper on the Run
description: A runaway from a summer camp ends up at the Stump, but Craig suspects her story may not be what it seems.

title: Shun Shine/Ronin Son
description: Shun Shine: The AO want to evolve their Bakugan like Dan did with Drago but only Shun finds a way by tapping into the energy of the Mind Core Cell./Ronin Son: When Shun's cousin Masato Kazami claims Hydorous as his intellectual property the AO must battle to keep their friend by their side.

title: This One Goes to 11
description: During one last stop by a toy store before Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max's maiden voyage across the Atlantic, Ben runs into an old bully, Kevin 11, who now has new powers. He's able to transform into aliens just like Ben, such as the "bootleg" doppelgänger of Cannonbolt— Wreckingbolt!

title: The Cringe
description: When the uncomfortableness between them reaches new levels, Gumball and Hot Dog Guy decide they have to confront their ongoing awkwardness by making things as awkward as possible.

title: Futbol a Muerte
description: Cuando Vic no elige a Val para su equipo de fútbol, Val promete ganar con su propio equipo. Pero cuando su equipo no está a la altura, recurre a medios sobrenaturales para ganar.

title: Questing For Quests
description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

title: Invasion of the Booger Snatchers
description: Harold believes that the picture day photographer is somehow turning the kids into well behaved zombies.

title: Girls Night In Part 2
description: When Blackfire begins her plan to conquer Earth, the girls must pull out all the stops to defeat her.

title: Booster's Gold
description: Green Arrow becomes involved with Booster Gold when he discovers that the self-centered superhero has brought dinosaurs back from the past for a money-making venture.

title: Roadtrip Ruckus
description: Richard has decided to take Unikitty and the gang for a pleasant and relaxing 10 hour road trip. At first everyone is against the trip, but they soon start to have fun. Unfortunately, their idea of fun is not Richard's.  He soon begins to give in to his inner road-rage. To make matters worse they are being chased by a killer semi-truck, and their car has been invaded by weird bug hitchhiker.  Will Richard loose it, or will the trip be a great success?

title: Movie Night
description: It's Movie Night and the Titans have a hard time deciding who gets to choose which movie they watch.

title: Dignity of Teeth
description: When Beast Boy gets a stack of cash from the Tooth Fairy, against Raven's advice the other Titans start knocking out their own teeth to get some of that sweet Tooth Fairy money.

title: Gum and Gummer
description: Beth gets her gum stuck in Leshawna's hair and has to get it out - without Leshawna finding out it's there.

title: It Was Them
description: Dr. Animo has escaped his Plumber prison, and Ben and Rook must track him down before he turns the world into his personal mutant ant farm! (Introducing Nemetrix alien Slamworm, Galvan Plumbers Blukic and Driba, Arctiguana, new Ben alien Crashhopper.)

title: Viaje en Carretera
description: Richard decidió llevar a Unikitty y a la banda a un agradable y relajante viaje de 10 horas por la carretera. Al principio todo el mundo está en contra del viaje, pero pronto empiezan a divertirse. Por desgracia, su idea de diversión no es la de Richard. Pronto, el conductor comienza a sucumbir ante su furia interior al volante. Para colmo de males, los persigue un semirremolque asesino, y su coche ha sido invadido por un extraño autoestopista. ¿Richard perderá la razón o el viaje será un gran éxito?

title: Unboxing Part 2
description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

title: 1992 Called
description: Uncle Grandpa travels back to the year 1492 to retrieve a pair of pants.

title: Big Reveal
description: KO finds out who his father is.

title: How to Build a Dragon
description: While Lloyd and the rebels celebrate their successful strike against Emperor Garmadon, in the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the Ninja dare an elaborate escape from the clutches of Iron Baron and his Dragon Hunters.

title: Jessica's Trail
description: Jessica wanders into an unfamiliar creek, leaving Craig to find her before his Mom notices!

title: El Elegido
description: Tobías intenta ser el mejor amigo de Gumball.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Snow Way Out
description: Owen wants everyone to love his new snowsuit and envy him, but it's just not working out that way.

title: It's Chemistry, Man
description: Chemistry Man lays siege to Silicon Central when he discovers that his replacement, Miss CHO, has been presented with a teaching award.

title: Cousin of the Creek
description: Craig takes his cousin, Bryson, to the Creek, and accidentally starts a water balloon war.

title: Bewitched, Bothered and Bothered Some More!
description: Flonk hires the Warriors to make Witch Way change his brother Helmut from a frog back to human.

title: The Gym
description: The Bears go to the gym and get quite the work out.

title: Catching the Wave
description: Pops wants to catch a wave.

title: Superman Red vs Superman Blue
description: Luthor comes up with the means to separate each Justice Leaguer in two, one passive and good, the other aggressive and mean.

title: Ben 4 Good Buddy
description: Out on a desert highway, a group of modern day highway pirates hijack the Rustbucket, trick it out and use it in a daring robbery. And while Ben and Gwen are at first glad to get rid of that "bucket of bolts", they come to realize the Rustbucket is "a part of the family." In the end our trio heroes get Max's beloved "ride" back and bring down these pirates once and for all.

title: Caveman
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to civilize a caveman so that Benson will let him stay at the park.

title: Two Lies, One Truth
description: As Lloyd unmasks Mystake for who she truly is, Emperor Garmadon embraces Harumi as his daughter of darkness. Meanwhile, Wu holds onto faith as he leads his friends into dangerous Oni territory in the hope of finding Firstbourne's nest

title: El Equipo Perfecto
description: A Cebollín le preocupa que su relación con Manzana corra peligro cuando un gato callejero entra en su vida.

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: Saturday School
description: After creating an unapproved mural on a wall at Aberdale Elementary, Clarence, Jeff and Sumo are forced to come to school on a Saturday to clean up as punishment.

title: Go With the Flow
description: When Sal stays with Vic & Val, the boys are annoyed by him as their roommate but eventually they learn how cool and magical he is.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: Propinas
description: Luego de destruir por accidente el boleto de Falafel para un concierto, Manzana y Cebollín deben descubrir un modo de evitar la furia de Falafel.

title: Hierro y piedra
description: Cole y Wu Joven intentan liberar a sus amigos, que han sido capturados por una tribu de Cazadores de Dragones. Mientras tanto en Ninjago, Lloyd se reúne con unos viejos amigos que quizás sean aliados valiosos contra el Emperador Garmadon.

title: A Cold Goodbye
description: Having learned Zane is not dead, Master Wu prepares to go after him, but Lloyd and the other ninja take matters into their own hands and defy their Master.

title: Steven Universe True Kinda Love Performance at San Diego Comic-Con
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar and Estelle perform a new song from Steven Universe the Movie at San Diego Comic-Con.

title: Salvando a Faith
description: Lloyd y su equipo planean tomar el control del Oni Titan. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, los Ninja caen en las garras del Barón de Hierro y un viejo maestro regresa.

title: Spice Game
description: Tired of Robin's bland cooking, the other Titans try their hand at spicing up their food.

title: Home on the Run/Top Slot
description: Home on the Run: We are introduced to Shun's mysterious backstory, his relationship with his industrialist father and desire for a closer knit family./Top Slot: Dan and Shun butt heads on how best to make the AO a real team amidst growing threats including the mysterious Shargo Ronin.

title: Sick Mao
description: When Mao Mao won't admit that he's sick, he puts the town in danger.

title: Green Destiny
description: The Ninja finally return home and unite to stop Emperor Garmadon, forcing Lloyd to make a decision that will forever change Ninjago.

title: Baby Orphan Ninja Bears
description: The Baby Bears venture into the sewers and meet a ninja-like martial arts master.

title: The Rival
description: The Wattersons look back on Anais' first days in the Watterson house. Gumball and Darwin quickly find themselves up an opponent who is able to outsmart them at every turn.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.

title: Lessons for a Master
description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

title: Anger Management
description: Aunt Grandma's back is causing more trouble for Uncle Grandpa.

title: Steven Universe Love Like You Performance at San Diego Comic-Con
description: Steven Universe creator Rebecca Sugar performs "Love Like You," from the end credits of Steven Universe at San Diego Comic-Con.

title: The Oct-Father
description: When Princess Morbucks steals Octi, Bubbles' reaction surprises everyone, even her sisters.

title: Los Vegetales
description: Gumball y Darwin solo quieren holgazanear todo el día, pero terminan teniendo que salvar al resto de la familia.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Afraid of the Dark
description: When UG helps a little girl who is afraid of the dark, he convinces her there's nothing to be afraid of but their imaginations.  But when their imaginations prove to be pretty terrifying, they go on a quest to turn on the lights.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Galactic Wonder
description: Wonder Woman has won student of the month at Super Hero High again!  As a special surprise Principal Waller has flown in Wonder Woman's mother, Queen Hippolyta, for a visit. Queen Hippolyta is not happy with what she finds and demands that Wonder Woman return to school at the island paradise of Themyscira. Hoping to take her mind off of her troubles with her mother Wonder Woman, Batgirl and Supergirl decide to investigate a strange electromagnetic anomaly. Their investigation leads them to the hideout of Lena Luthor where they discover a plot between her and Eclipso to transform the planet Earth into a new version of Gemworld!  The girls will have to split up to find the generators scattered around the planet and destroy them. They'll also have to overcome Lena's new breed of mood altering Kryptomites to save the day and convince Queen Hippolyta that Super Hero High is the best school for Wonder Woman!

title: All Up in Your Drill
description: Duncan stages a small coup to oust Courtney as their official class firefighter so that he can wear the shiny firefighter helmet - until he smells smoke in the classroom and begs her to take her job back.

title: Steven Universe: Behind the Curtain Trailer
description: Get a sneak peek at the team who created Steven Universe the Movie in this trailer for a behind-the-scenes documentary.

title: Puhoy
description: Stuck inside the treehouse during a sword storm, Jake builds a pillow fort while Finn goes to a different world.

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.

title: Career Opportunities/Punch the Clock
description: Career Opportunities: After defeating Magnus the AO get an offer of employment from a surprising source Philomena Dusk!/Punch the Clock: During a commercial to celebrate their joining the AAAnimus team Dan and the AO rebel before they sellout.

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: The Stayover
description: After going overboard on the candy, Blossom and Buttercup wake up with no memory of last night and no idea where Bubbles is! They must piece together the events of last night and find Bubbles before the Professor gets back!

title: Pachydermus Packard and the Camp of Fantasy
description: A doctor orders Mr. Pachydermus to have an adventure, so he attends the Warriors' super-annoying, "Fantasy Camp"!

title: #SweetJustice Part 1
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Falafel's Fun Day
description: When Falafel decides to pack up and leave the city, Apple and Onion have to convince him to stay or they'll have to leave too.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: Aunt Grandma
description: The gang must stop a nefarious imposter from rendering Uncle Grandpa obsolete.

title: Gem Drill
description: Steven takes a journey deep underground.

title: All Aboard the Space Train
description: In a strange turn of events, the JLA enlist the help of Space Cabbie and Jonah Hex to stop the hijacking of an intergalactic space train.

title: Too Much Is Never Enough
description: Envious of Namagem's ability to wield more than three powers at a time, Mega Man tries taking all of his replicated schematics on board, with grave side effects.

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: Ricardio the Heart Guy
description: Finn becomes jealous of Princes Bubblegum's new suitor.

title: #LaDulceJusticia - Segunda parte
description: Cuando seis chicas comunes y corrientes descubren que cada una tiene un poder extraordinario diferente, deciden unir fuerzas para derrotar a algunos de los villanos más siniestros de Metrópolis en la parte 2 del episodio estreno.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Mr. Moon/What's Wrong with Dan
description: Mr. Moon: Wynton finds a new Bakugan who proves difficult to control but things get more complicated when Col. Tripp seizes control of Trox./What's Wrong with Dan: With "Dan" behaving strangely toward the AO Lightning sniffs out the truth- an impostor!

title: Tooth Trouble
description: Puppycorn loses his first tooth and Unikitty's excited for her little bro, now he​ ​gets a visit from​ ​the​ ​legendary Tooth Fairy!​ ​But when the Tooth Fairy is a no-show, Unikitty and her friends take on the mantle and responsibilities. But will they play too fast and loose with loose teeth and hit a raw nerve?

title: Lying Around the House/Bubble Boy
description: Lying Around The House: The girls tell little white lies that turn into a big, bad problem./Bubble Boy: Realizing that the only way to beat the Rowdyruff Boys is to join them, Bubbles takes Boomer's place in this rough-and-tumble band of boys.

title: Polos Opuestos
description: Un viaje al Polo Sur queda patas arriba cuando el equipo Tennyson aterriza en el Polo Norte. Pero Ben rápidamente descubre a los culpables: iSolar y Polar Twain, unos científicos con poder magnético que quieren chantajear al mundo amenazando con invertir los polos magnéticos de la Tierra!

title: Dos mentiras una verdad
description: Cuando Lloyd desenmascara y revela la identidad de Mystake, el Emperador Garmadon acepta a Harumi como su hija de la oscuridad. Mientras tanto, Wu se aferra a su fe al llevar a sus amigos hacia territorios Oni peligrosos esperando encontrar el nido de la Primogénita.

title: Wasted True Potential
description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

title: I Love You Mao Mao
description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.

title: Deep Space Vacation
description: When Gar lets KO and Enid take a vacation to outer  space, they get more than they bargained for.

title: The One
description: Gumball and Darwin are joking around, but when Tobias joins in and makes fun of Gumball, he's incredibly offended. They explain to Tobias that to make those jokes he'd need to be higher on Gumball's friend list. They think that's the end of it, but Tobias is after that number one spot.

title: Bubble
description: Panda becomes a germophobe and decides to live the rest of his life in a bubble.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: El Rival
description: Volvemos a la época en la que Anaís era una bebé recién nacida, y los celos de Gumball y Darwin desatan una guerra de bebés.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.

title: The Sucker
description: Gumball spends the day with Bomb Kid, who has decided Gumball is the perfect target for him and his friends to play pranks on. However he soon learns that Gumball is so gullible that pranks bounce off him.

title: Destino verde
description: Los Ninjas regresan por fin a casa y se unen para detener al Emperador Garmadon, obligando a Lloyd a tomar una decisión que cambiará por siempre a Ninjago.

title: Ocean of Fear
description: Finn faces his biggest challenge yet...overcoming his fear of water.

title: Una Nueva Vida
description: Manzana y Cebollín abandonan sus hogares y se mudan a la ciudad, donde se conocen por primera vez.

title: Aluxes
description: Vic encuentra una antigua reliquia que invoca a una pandilla de traviesas criaturas, iy las consecuencias son desastrosas!
